TAMP:20210928T161650Z\r\nUID:imlfq3beoo6kvs6kkhl9874c44@google.com\r\nCREATED:20210921T060322Z\r\nX-LIC-ERROR;X-LIC-ERRORTYPE=VALUE-PARSE-ERROR:No value for DESCRIPTION \r\n property. Removing entire property:\r\nLAST-MODIFIED:20210928T161650Z\r\nX-LIC-ERROR;X-LIC-ERRORTYPE=VALUE-PARSE-ERROR:No value for LOCATION \r\n property. Removing entire property:\r\nSEQUENCE:0\r\nSTATUS:CONFIRMED\r\nSUMMARY:Contracting Standup\r\nTRANSP:OPAQUE\r\nX-APPLE-TRAVEL-ADVISORY-BEHAVIOR:AUTOMATIC\r\nX-EVOLUTION-CALDAV-ETAG:63768529010\r\nBEGIN:VALARM\r\nACTION:DISPLAY\r\nDESCRIPTION:This is an event reminder\r\nTRIGGER:-PT15M\r\nX-EVOLUTION-ALARM-UID:a46ca245b777425c5a1c87d8817fcaf5e115d9db\r\nEND:VALARM\r\nBEGIN:VALARM\r\nACTION:NONE\r\nTRIGGER;VALUE=DATE-TIME:19760401T005545Z\r\nX-WR-ALARMUID:A81C7DDC-297F-4C7B-9743-E3115EC83521\r\nUID:A81C7DDC-297F-4C7B-9743-E3115EC83521\r\nACKNOWLEDGED:20210928T161555Z\r\nX-APPLE-DEFAULT-ALARM:TRUE\r\nX-EVOLUTION-ALARM-UID:a3967f2ea915f597c3bc726d980c7baf4409a67f\r\nEND:VALARM\r\nEND:VEVENT\r\n', '3d0b82a3d06f2e4d345197b35b0f1425a406f559\n0c3a373ce41ecc99d5277bf4228dbdfc85ef01d4\t20211012T080000\n1634050200\n1634050800\n1634054400\nBEGIN:VEVENT\r\nDTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210511T080000\r\nDTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210511T090000\r\nRRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;INTERVAL=2;BYDAY=TU\r\nDTSTAMP:20210825T222801Z\r\nORGANIZER;CN=climate-sig@lists.hyperledger.org:mailto:\r\n climate-sig@lists.hyperledger.org\r\nUID:DZWx.1618238562098014154.uc6u@lists.hyperledger.org\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED;\r\n CN=jon@sno.llc;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:jon@sno.llc\r\nCREATED:20210825T222742Z\r\nDESCRIPTION:The biweekly Standards WG workshop will carry out the work \r\n plan as set out in this ( https:\r\n //drive.google.com/file/d/1luI_bR3RdXP9EBxsQ58PQMdRKwREkvwm/view?usp=shari\r\n ng ) document.\\n\\nThis involves four phases:\\nA. Conceptualisation of a \r\n DLT-enabled standardisation architecture to streamline Climate Action & \r\n Accounting.\\nB. Implementing the result of phase A in three different \r\n paradigms: as a relational database\\, as a Radix-Merkle tree (as is used \r\n by Hyperledger Sawtooth)\\, and as a token-and-smart-contract network \r\n (possibly DAML).\\nC. Testing applicability to real-life use cases.\\nD. \r\n Reviewing the results from phase C and revisiting phases A-C as \r\n necessary.\\n\\nAnyone is welcome to join\\, but we are specifically looking \r\n for individuals interested in the fundamentals of climate accounting and \r\n climate-related MRV\\, or individuals who seek to develop or contribute \r\n skills in DLT networks and/or relational database design within the \r\n context of climate action and accounting.\\n\\nThe call will take place \r\n every other Tuesday at 7 AM pacific (i.e. on the weeks between the \r\n standard CA2SIG calls).\\n\\nMore about the Standards group is at: https:\r\n //wiki.hyperledger.org/display/CASIG/Standards+WG\r\nLAST-MODIFIED:20210825T222801Z\r\nLOCATION:https:\r\n //zoom.us/my/hyperledger.community.backup?pwd=dkJKdHRlc3dNZEdKR1JYdW40R2pD\r\n UT09\r\nSEQUENCE:0\r\nSTATUS:CONFIRMED\r\nSUMMARY:CA2SIG Standards WG call\r\nTRANSP:OPAQUE\r\nX-APPLE-TRAVEL-ADVISORY-BEHAVIOR:AUTOMATIC\r\nX-GIOIDS:Repeat:36679\r\nX-EVOLUTION-CALDAV-ETAG:63765613681\r\nBEGIN:VALARM\r\nACTION:DISPLAY\r\nDESCRIPTION:This is an event reminder\r\nTRIGGER:-PT10M\r\nX-EVOLUTION-ALARM-UID:0c3a373ce41ecc99d5277bf4228dbdfc85ef01d4\r\nEND:VALARM\r\nEND:VEVENT\r\n', 'f63ec81625fde854c1905233ed5e244dda3df917\n74a616d3484a52368554e3b8774db61e5e4187b0\t20211012T080000\n1634050200\n1634050800\n1634054400\nBEGIN:VEVENT\r\nDTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20211012T080000\r\nDTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20211012T090000\r\nDTSTAMP:20211011T234008Z\r\nORGANIZER;CN=tim.mather@fortiumpartners.com:mailto:\r\n tim.mather@fortiumpartners.com\r\nUID:23bptccqodcckdg64a2g06o2cu@google.com\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED;\r\n CN=tim.mather@fortiumpartners.com;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:\r\n tim.mather@fortiumpartners.com\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=NEEDS-ACTION;\r\n CN=All Fortium;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:all-fortium@fortiumpartners.com\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=DECLINED;\r\n CN=jonathan.azoff@fortiumpartners.com;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:\r\n jonathan.azoff@fortiumpartners.com\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED;CN=John \r\n Johnston;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:john@johnstonconsultants.com\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=DECLINED;\r\n CN=Michael Wilson;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:michael.w.wilson@outlook.com\r\nCREATED:20210909T172107Z\r\nDESCRIPTION:We´re back!  The security practice is back from a summer \r\n break.\\n\\nIn this month´s session\\, partner Tim Mather will discuss a \r\n growing scourage in the IT community - vendor security ratings companies \r\n (BitSight and Security Scorecard).  The extortion that these companies \r\n attempt will be explained\\, and how to help your clients fight \r\n back.\\n\\nFortium Partners le está invitando a una reunión de Zoom \r\n programada.\\n\\nTema: Security Practice Weekly Call\\nHora: Este es una \r\n reunión recurrente Reunirse en cualquier momento\\n\\nUnirse a la reunión \r\n Zoom\\nhttps:\r\n //us02web.zoom.us/j/87141987568?pwd=RitkdldhTndTZTdaT2hWRTJVSDRHUT09\\n\\nID\r\n  de reunión: 871 4198 7568\\nCódigo de acceso: fortiumsec\\nMóvil con un \r\n toque\\n+16699009128\\,\\,87141987568# Estados Unidos (San \r\n Jose)\\n+12532158782\\,\\,87141987568# Estados Unidos (Tacoma)\\n\\nMarcar \r\n según su ubicación\\n        +1 669 900 9128 Estados Unidos (San Jose)\\n \r\n        +1 253 215 8782 Estados Unidos (Tacoma)\\n        +1 346 248 7799 \r\n Estados Unidos (Houston)\\n        +1 646 558 8656 Estados Unidos (New \r\n York)\\n        +1 301 715 8592 Estados Unidos (Washington DC)\\n        +1 \r\n 312 626 6799 Estados Unidos (Chicago)\\nID de reunión: 871 4198 \r\n 7568\\nEncuentre su número local: https://us02web.zoom.us/u/kel6vqIQbF\r\nLAST-MODIFIED:20211011T234008Z\r\nLOCATION:https:\r\n //us02web.zoom.us/j/87141987568?pwd=RitkdldhTndTZTdaT2hWRTJVSDRHUT09\r\nSEQUENCE:0\r\nSTATUS:CONFIRMED\r\nSUMMARY:Security Q&A\r\nTRANSP:OPAQUE\r\nX-EVOLUTION-CALDAV-ETAG:63769678808\r\nBEGIN:VALARM\r\nACTION:DISPLAY\r\nDESCRIPTION:This is an event reminder\r\nTRIGGER:-PT10M\r\nX-EVOLUTION-ALARM-UID:74a616d3484a52368554e3b8774db61e5e4187b0\r\nEND:VALARM\r\nEND:VEVENT\r\n', '3d0b82a3d06f2e4d345197b35b0f1425a406f559\ndcc9a04a3cd4f6e7a422d78165f0b4937889b5d8\t20211011T170000\n1633995900\n1633996800\n1634000400\nBEGIN:VEVENT\r\nDTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210705T170000\r\nDTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210705T180000\r\nRRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=MO,TU,WE,TH,FR\r\nDTSTAMP:20211011T161733Z\r\nUID:6cv8je86jcreqdhegofuoftdt1@google.com\r\nCREATED:20210623T045249Z\r\nX-LIC-ERROR;X-LIC-ERRORTYPE=VALUE-PARSE-ERROR:No value for DESCRIPTION \r\n property. Removing entire property:\r\nLAST-MODIFIED:20211011T161733Z\r\nX-LIC-ERROR;X-LIC-ERRORTYPE=VALUE-PARSE-ERROR:No value for LOCATION \r\n property. Removing entire property:\r\nSEQUENCE:1\r\nSTATUS:CONFIRMED\r\nSUMMARY:Family Time\r\nTRANSP:OPAQUE\r\nX-APPLE-TRAVEL-ADVISORY-BEHAVIOR:AUTOMATIC\r\nX-LIC-ERROR;X-LIC-ERRORTYPE=VALUE-PARSE-ERROR:No value for LOCATION \r\n property. Removing entire property:\r\nX-EVOLUTION-CALDAV-ETAG:63769652253\r\nBEGIN:VALARM\r\nACTION:DISPLAY\r\nDESCRIPTION:This is an event reminder\r\nTRIGGER:-PT15M\r\nX-EVOLUTION-ALARM-UID:dcc9a04a3cd4f6e7a422d78165f0b4937889b5d8\r\nEND:VALARM\r\nBEGIN:VALARM\r\nACTION:NONE\r\nTRIGGER;VALUE=DATE-TIME:19760401T005545Z\r\nX-WR-ALARMUID:47982E63-BBE2-4F6F-B2A3-F239A9B86910\r\nUID:47982E63-BBE2-4F6F-B2A3-F239A9B86910\r\nACKNOWLEDGED:20210916T235647Z\r\nX-APPLE-DEFAULT-ALARM:TRUE\r\nX-EVOLUTION-ALARM-UID:e99962ec451d62f2596251148717ce5fd68408a3\r\nEND:VALARM\r\nEND:VEVENT\r\n', '67efbf0ad04d840b4435a4c