/chat?ref=calendar">Chat</a>\r\nLAST-MODIFIED:20210929T034834Z\r\nX-LIC-ERROR;X-LIC-ERRORTYPE=VALUE-PARSE-ERROR:No value for LOCATION \r\n property. Removing entire property:\r\nSEQUENCE:0\r\nSTATUS:CONFIRMED\r\nSUMMARY:Lunchclub - Jason <> Jonathan\r\nTRANSP:OPAQUE\r\nX-EVOLUTION-CALDAV-ETAG:63768570514\r\nBEGIN:VALARM\r\nACTION:DISPLAY\r\nDESCRIPTION:This is an event reminder\r\nTRIGGER:-PT1H\r\nX-EVOLUTION-ALARM-UID:373e4946c9845bdb822addc4f9921cb0b3a9912e\r\nEND:VALARM\r\nBEGIN:VALARM\r\nACTION:DISPLAY\r\nDESCRIPTION:This is an event reminder\r\nTRIGGER:-PT2H\r\nX-EVOLUTION-ALARM-UID:5c92163fe2054ebcf711521cd657bfb3e3cf48d7\r\nEND:VALARM\r\nEND:VEVENT\r\n', "f63ec81625fde854c1905233ed5e244dda3df917\n68c080ba1939fdd15a1b21f4cd506cd8d2bfc2a8\t20211001T150000\n1633117800\n1633118400\n1633122000\nBEGIN:VEVENT\r\nDTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20210813T150000\r\nDTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20210813T160000\r\nRRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=FR\r\nDTSTAMP:20210930T155653Z\r\nORGANIZER;CN=Burke Autrey:mailto:burke.autrey@fortiumpartners.com\r\nUID:8jmgvv34d2ei3fku61lgaqd0o4_R20210813T200000@google.com\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=NEEDS-ACTION;\r\n CN=All Fortium;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:all-fortium@fortiumpartners.com\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED;\r\n CN=Burke Autrey;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:burke.autrey@fortiumpartners.com\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=TENTATIVE;\r\n CN=steve cooper;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:\r\n steve.cooper@strategicinformationconcepts.com\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED;\r\n CN=jonathan.azoff@fortiumpartners.com;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:\r\n jonathan.azoff@fortiumpartners.com\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED;\r\n CN=Louis Hyman;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:louis@idealhealth.tech\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=DECLINED;\r\n CN=Michael Wilson;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:michael.w.wilson@outlook.com\r\nCREATED:20201030T205639Z\r\nDESCRIPTION:<br>Partners - this is just a way for us to stay \r\n connected.&nbsp\\; If you can make it\\, join us.&nbsp\\; If not\\, we \r\n understand.&nbsp\\;<br><br>Guidelines:<br><ul><li>We can talk about work \r\n and the firm but my main goal is to see if this can make the Firm feel \r\n smaller\\, more connected\\, and more like a community.</li><li>Turn on \r\n your camera if you want.&nbsp\\; Feels more like a social gathering if you \r\n do.</li><li>Mute if you're not talking but if it's quiet (and you don't \r\n have a cough)\\, leave your line open so the conversation is more \r\n natural.</li><li>Chat to individuals or the group to expand the \r\n conversation</li><li>Tell us what's going on</li><li>For the larger \r\n group\\, let's avoid political conversations\\, digs\\, positioning\\, \r\n etc.&nbsp\\; Feel free to schedule your own get-together for that! :\r\n -)</li></ul>We'll keep doing this until nobody comes anymore or we have a \r\n better idea (suggestions \r\n welcome)!<br><br>Burke<br>──────────<br>Burke Autrey \r\n is inviting you to a scheduled Zoom meeting.<br><br>Join Zoom \r\n Meeting<br><a href=\"https:\r\n //us02web.zoom.us/j/776621272?pwd=WVA2VlM0YXlwMjQvbHFzZEc0YVdwdz09\">https:\r\n //us02web.zoom.us/j/776621272?pwd=WVA2VlM0YXlwMjQvbHFzZEc0YVdwdz09</a><br>\r\n <br>Meeting ID: 776 621 272<br>Passcode: 142297<br>One tap \r\n mobile<br>+13462487799\\,\\,776621272# US \r\n (Houston)<br>+12532158782\\,\\,776621272# US (Tacoma)<br><br>Dial by your \r\n location<br>&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;+1 \r\n 346 248 7799 US (Houston)<br>&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;\r\n &nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;+1 253 215 8782 US (Tacoma)<br>&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;\r\n &nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;+1 669 900 9128 US (San Jose)<br>&nbsp\\;\r\n &nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;+1 646 558 8656 US (New \r\n York)<br>&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp\\;&nbsp