/Los_Angeles:20210921T091500\r\nDTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210921T093000\r\nRRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=MO,TU,WE\r\nDTSTAMP:20210927T162716Z\r\nUID:imlfq3beoo6kvs6kkhl9874c44@google.com\r\nCREATED:20210921T060322Z\r\nX-LIC-ERROR;X-LIC-ERRORTYPE=VALUE-PARSE-ERROR:No value for DESCRIPTION \r\n property. Removing entire property:\r\nLAST-MODIFIED:20210927T162716Z\r\nX-LIC-ERROR;X-LIC-ERRORTYPE=VALUE-PARSE-ERROR:No value for LOCATION \r\n property. Removing entire property:\r\nSEQUENCE:0\r\nSTATUS:CONFIRMED\r\nSUMMARY:Contracting Standup\r\nTRANSP:OPAQUE\r\nX-APPLE-TRAVEL-ADVISORY-BEHAVIOR:AUTOMATIC\r\nX-EVOLUTION-CALDAV-ETAG:63768443236\r\nBEGIN:VALARM\r\nACTION:DISPLAY\r\nDESCRIPTION:This is an event reminder\r\nTRIGGER:-PT15M\r\nX-EVOLUTION-ALARM-UID:125e50fbcea143fee6e62389471576e1e93b8d3b\r\nEND:VALARM\r\nBEGIN:VALARM\r\nACTION:NONE\r\nTRIGGER;VALUE=DATE-TIME:19760401T005545Z\r\nX-WR-ALARMUID:A81C7DDC-297F-4C7B-9743-E3115EC83521\r\nUID:A81C7DDC-297F-4C7B-9743-E3115EC83521\r\nACKNOWLEDGED:20210927T162715Z\r\nX-APPLE-DEFAULT-ALARM:TRUE\r\nX-EVOLUTION-ALARM-UID:a96f901596b763c385ca75bf924fd296ffe6a9b2\r\nEND:VALARM\r\nEND:VEVENT\r\n', '3d0b82a3d06f2e4d345197b35b0f1425a406f559\n0c3a373ce41ecc99d5277bf4228dbdfc85ef01d4\t20210928T080000\n1632840600\n1632841200\n1632844800\nBEGIN:VEVENT\r\nDTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210511T080000\r\nDTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210511T090000\r\nRRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;INTERVAL=2;BYDAY=TU\r\nDTSTAMP:20210825T222801Z\r\nORGANIZER;CN=climate-sig@lists.hyperledger.org:mailto:\r\n climate-sig@lists.hyperledger.org\r\nUID:DZWx.1618238562098014154.uc6u@lists.hyperledger.org\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED;\r\n CN=jon@sno.llc;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:jon@sno.llc\r\nCREATED:20210825T222742Z\r\nDESCRIPTION:The biweekly Standards WG workshop will carry out the work \r\n plan as set out in this ( https:\r\n //drive.google.com/file/d/1luI_bR3RdXP9EBxsQ58PQMdRKwREkvwm/view?usp=shari\r\n ng ) document.\\n\\nThis involves four phases:\\nA. Conceptualisation of a \r\n DLT-enabled standardisation architecture to streamline Climate Action & \r\n Accounting.\\nB. Implementing the result of phase A in three different \r\n paradigms: as a relational database\\, as a Radix-Merkle tree (as is used \r\n by Hyperledger Sawtooth)\\, and as a token-and-smart-contract network \r\n (possibly DAML).\\nC. Testing applicability to real-life use cases.\\nD. \r\n Reviewing the results from phase C and revisiting phases A-C as \r\n necessary.\\n\\nAnyone is welcome to join\\, but we are specifically looking \r\n for individuals interested in the fundamentals of climate accounting and \r\n climate-related MRV\\, or individuals who seek to develop or contribute \r\n skills in DLT networks and/or relational database design within the \r\n context of climate action and accounting.\\n\\nThe call will take place \r\n every other Tuesday at 7 AM pacific (i.e. on the weeks between the \r\n standard CA2SIG calls).\\n\\nMore about the Standards group is at: https:\r\n //wiki.hyperledger.org/display/CASIG/Standards+WG\r\nLAST-MODIFIED:20210825T222801Z\r\nLOCATION:https:\r\n //zoom.us/my/hyperledger.community.backup?pwd=dkJKdHRlc3dNZEdKR1JYdW40R2pD\r\n UT09\r\nSEQUENCE:0\r\nSTATUS:CONFIRMED\r\nSUMMARY:CA2SIG Standards WG call\r\nTRANSP:OPAQUE\r\nX-APPLE-TRAVEL-ADVISORY-BEHAVIOR:AUTOMATIC\r\nX-GIOIDS:Repeat:36679\r\nX-EVOLUTION-CALDAV-ETAG:63765613681\r\nBEGIN:VALARM\r\nACTION:DISPLAY\r\nDESCRIPTION:This is an event reminder\r\nTRIGGER:-PT10M\r\nX-EVOLUTION-ALARM-UID:0c3a373ce41ecc99d5277bf4228dbdfc85ef01d4\r\nEND:VALARM\r\nEND:VEVENT\r\n', "3d0b82a3d06f2e4d345197b35b0f1425a406f559\n88531a5978cefd2db7dfa4a9aed68063fca8dec1\t20210928T080000\n1632840600\n1632841200\n1632844800\nBEGIN:VEVENT\r\nDTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210928T080000\r\nDTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210928T090000\r\nDTSTAMP:20210928T134722Z\r\nORGANIZER;CN=ODCT GLOBAL:mailto:\r\n c_4qpp1oqem5g266l4k4i6dn8j7s@group.calendar.google.com\r\nUID:2dbogpepvpoo0v5ju7hdg9cacu@google.com\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED;\r\n CN=jon@sno.llc;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:jon@sno.llc\r\nCREATED:20210914T121210Z\r\nDESCRIPTION:<b>Want to know more about On Deck&nbsp\\;Climate&nbsp\\;Tech \r\n (ODCT)? Join us for this Q&amp\\;A!</b><br>\u200b <br>On Deck&nbsp\\;\r\n Climate&nbsp\\;Tech is a is a continuous community for startup and&nbsp\\;\r\n climate&nbsp\\;experts to come together to build\\, join\\, or support \r\n revolutionary climate tech startups. Our next onboarding cohort is \r\n kicking off on October 23rd! You can learn more at:&nbsp\\; <a href=\"http:\r\n ///\">beondeck.com/climate</a><br>\u200b <br>&nbsp\\;This public Q&amp\\;A is a \r\n space for you to learn more about the&nbsp\\;ODCT&nbsp\\;program\\, assess \r\n whether it's a good fit\\, and share your personal goals that will help us \r\n shape our program curriculum. Please join us whether you've applied\\, are \r\n considering applying or just want to learn more.<br>\u200b <br>Can’t make \r\n it live? You should still RSVP\\, we’ll send a recording. We look \r\n forward to hosting you!<br><br><b><a href=\"https:\r\n //beondeck.zoom.us/j/94132179199?pwd=QW0xMVhNQU1vS0ltWWFqWGZNeHordz09\" \r\n id=\"ow2848\" __is_owner=\"true\">Zoom Link</a> | Password: odct</b>\r\nLAST-MODIFIED:20210928T134722Z\r\nLOCATION:https:\r\n //beondeck.zoom.us/j/94132179199?pwd=QW0xMVhNQU1vS0ltWWFqWGZNeHordz09\r\nSEQUENCE:0\r\nSTATUS:CONFIRMED\r\nSUMMARY:On Deck Climate Tech Q&A\r\nTRANSP:OPAQUE\r\nX-EVOLUTION-CALDAV-ETAG:63768520042\r\nBEGIN:VALARM\r\nACTION:DISPLAY\r\nDESCRIPTION:This is an event reminder\r\nTRIGGER:-PT10M\r\nX-EVOLUTION-ALARM-UID:88531a5978cefd2db7dfa4a9aed68063fca8dec1\r\nEND:VALARM\r\nEND:VEVENT\r\n", '67efbf0ad04d840b4435a4c0baf89703f8aa0ceb\nd54c66c5d07fddf6ffe3cf1b7dd9f99e012d6315\t20210927T193000\n1632795300\n1632796200\n1632801600\nBEGIN:VEVENT\r\nDTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210802T193000\r\nDTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210802T210000\r\nRRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY\r\nDTSTAMP:20210907T035145Z\r\nUID:fcdc1425453845ad989fdba383cf1c94\r\nCREATED:20210802T190420Z\r\nX-LIC-ERROR;X-LIC-ERRORTYPE=VALUE-PARSE-ERROR:No value for DESCRIPTION \r\n property. Removing entire property:\r\nLAST-MODIFIED:20210907T035145Z\r\nX-LIC-ERROR;X-LIC-ERRORTYPE=VALUE-PARSE-ERROR:No value for LOCATION \r\n property. Removing entire property:\r\nSEQUENCE:0\r\nSTATUS:CONFIRMED\r\nSUMMARY:BBall @ STC\r\nTRANSP:OPAQUE\r\nX-APPLE-TRAVEL-ADVISORY-BEHAVIOR:AUTOMATIC\r\nX-EVOLUTION-CALDAV-ETAG:63766669905\r\nBEGIN:VALARM\r\nACTION:DISPLAY\r\nDESCRIPTION:This is an event reminder\r\nTRIGGER:-PT15M\r\nX-EVOLUTION-ALARM-UID:d54c66c5d07fddf6ffe3cf1b7dd9f99e012d6315\r\nEND:VALARM\r\nBEGIN:VALARM\r\nACTION:NONE\r\nTRIGGER;VALUE=DATE-TIME:19760401T005545Z\r\nX-WR-ALARMUID:A70B1E1F-A84E-4DEC-8696-3E81F75674DD\r\nUID:A70B1E1F-A84E-4DEC-8696-3E81F75674DD\r\nACKNOWLEDGED:20210907T035145Z\r\nX-APPLE-DEFAULT-ALARM:TRUE\r\nX-EVOLUTION-ALARM-UID:edba36605665d232e7f610c7215ebccf269c8951\r\nEND:VALARM\r\nEND:VEVENT\r\n', '3d0b82a3d06f2e4d345197b35b0f1425a406f559\n5b945fd9fc5c584ca27b374bfe97cc7240fd1ae0\t20210927T170000\n1632786300\n1632787200\n1632790800\nBEGIN:VEVENT\r\nDTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210705T170000\r\nDTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210705T180000\r\nRRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=MO,TU,WE,TH,FR\r\nDTSTAMP:20210916T235648Z\r\nUID:6cv8je86jcreqdhegofuoftdt1@google.com\r\nCREATED:20210623T045249Z\r\nX-LIC-ERROR;X-LIC-ERRORTYPE=VALUE-PARSE-ERROR:No value for DESCRIPTION \r\n property. Removing entire property:\r\nLAST-MODIFIED:20210916T235648Z\r\nX-LIC-ERROR;X-LIC-ERRORTYPE=VALUE-PARSE-ERROR:No value for LOCATION \r\n property. Removing entire property:\r\nSEQUENCE:1\r\nSTATUS:CONFIRMED\r\nSUMMARY:Family Time\r\nTRANSP:OPAQUE\r\nX-APPLE-TRAVEL-ADVISORY-BEHAVIOR:AUTOMATIC\r\nX-EVOLUTION-CALDAV-ETAG:63767519808\r\nBEGIN:VALARM\r\nACTION:DISPLAY\r\nDESCRIPTION:This is an event reminder\r\nTRIGGER:-PT15M\r\nX-EV